  "title": "Facilities Maintenance Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in maintaining of building facilities on timely - servicing, inspection, equipment re-certification etc..</li>\n  <li>Undertake minor repair and maintenance work.</li>\n  <li>Conduct daily facilities inspection to identify any defect</li>\n  <li>Determine and analyze the cause of defects, breakdowns and faults &amp; provide suggestions to prevent any future occurrences</li>\n  <li>Liaise and supervise contractors on facilities repair / renovation works to ensure acceptable standard of work</li>\n  <li>Ensure that only authorize users have accessed to locked venue</li>\n  <li>Other tasks as assigned by the Management</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma holder in M&amp;E / Civil Engineering or its equivalent</li>\n  <li>2 years of work experience in Facilities &amp; Building Management</li>\n  <li>Can work under minimal supervision and is pro-active</li>\n</ul>",
